<body>
<header>
  <h1 class="title"><img id="login-logo" src="/images/logo.png"><span id="title">WaypointsApp<span></h1>  
</header>
  <div id="homepage">
      <div id="login-info">
        <p>Waypoints is a simple WebApp that allows users to create itineraries, routes, and waypoints for a multitude of different events.<br /><br />Whether you're a tourist planning out a day trip, a bike messenger mapping out your delivery schedule, or a dog walker planning your pet visits, Waypoints stores, displays, and allows for easy access and editing to a visual representation of your routes.</p>
      </div>
      <div id="log-content">
        <img id="login-shot" src="/images/screenshot.png">
        <ul id="log-list-ul">
          <li class="log-list">Visual representation of current location</li>
          <li class="log-list">Create and save multiple routes</li>
          <li class="log-list">Add, delete and edit current waypoint route</li>
          <li class="log-list">Plan your trips weeks in advance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div id="login-button-div">
        <h3 style="display: inline-block;">Login via: <a id="login-button" href="/auth/google">Google+</a></h3>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
